<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">Contact</span>
    <h1>Get in touch.</h1>
    <p>
      Have a question, suggestion, or issue with one of the tools? Send a message and we will review it as soon as possible.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-tight">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card card-pad">
      <h2 class="section-title">Contact form</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        Use this form for tool feedback, article suggestions, bug reports, partnership questions, or general messages about UD Marketing Tools. Clear details help us understand the request faster, especially if you are reporting a problem with a specific page or tool.
      </p>

      <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xykvdaja" method="POST">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Name</label>
          <input id="name" name="name" type="text" class="tool-input">
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input id="email" name="email" type="email" class="tool-input">
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" class="tool-input" rows="6"></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-actions" style="margin-bottom:0;">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Message</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="card card-pad" style="margin-top:24px;">
      <h2 class="section-title">What to include</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        If you are asking about a tool, include the tool name and the page URL if possible. If something did not work as expected, explain what you entered, what result you expected, and what happened instead. For article or SEO topic suggestions, share the keyword, topic idea, or example you want us to consider.
      </p>
      <p class="section-desc">
        UD Marketing Tools is built around practical utilities for SEO, content writing, campaign tracking, QR codes, and marketing calculations. Feedback from real users helps us improve existing tools and decide which new guides or features should be added next.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
